xmp

Enum XmpProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<XmpProperty>
      • xmp.XmpProperty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<XmpProperty>

    public enum XmpProperty
extends java.lang.Enum<XmpProperty>
    Represents a fixed set of known XMP properties and their corresponding namespaces. This enum provides a type-safe way to handle XMP schema names, enabling efficient lookup and preventing errors from misspelled strings.
    Since:
    25 September 2025
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Trevor Maggs
